name: apply
description: Apply <callable> to the arguments stored in the <obj-argument-list> list.

name: compile
description: Convert <quoted-escm-expression> into a list of its equivalent bytecode instructions.

name: eval
description:
Evaluate <quoted-escm-expression> to produce a result. Equivalent to:
  (eval-bytecode (compile <quoted-escm-expression>))

name: gensym
description:
Returns a fresh, unique symbol. Guarentees that the symbol is unique across
threads as well. Used extensively by macros.

name: syntax?
description: Returns whether <macro-name-symbol> is a valid macro name.

name: expand-syntax
description: Returns the expansion of <quoted-macro-expression> by executing its macro.

name: delete-syntax!
description:
Remove <macro-name-symbol> from the compiler's macro registry.
Returns whether succeeded in removal. Used for macro localization.
